          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Normal Attack</span><br>Deals 2 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Physical DMG</span>.<br></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/17/35428890/f0d674be287c96be7066ab5e4e75b0fb_906037095217222440.png",
                "id": "talent30990",
                "key": "Card Force Translocation",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Card Force Translocation"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Normal Attack</span><br>Deals 2 <span style=\"color: #FF9999\">Pyro DMG</span>, summons a <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Grin-Malkin Hat</span>, and gains 1 stack of <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Prop Surplus</span>.<br>If this character has at least 6 HP, then they deal 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Piercing DMG</span> to themself.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Prop Surplus</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Prop Surplus</span> can stack up to 3 times.<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">When this character uses Bewildering Lights:</span> +1 DMG for each <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Prop Surplus</span> stack. After the skill is finalized, consume all <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Prop Surplus</span>, healing 1 HP for this character per stack.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/17/35428890/67d6f9d70e695a791caa42953d11e1e3_8296066126429552160.png",
                "id": "talent60882",
                "key": "Prop Arrow",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Prop Arrow"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Deals 3 <span style=\"color: #FF9999\">Pyro DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/17/35428890/053697dd2072f984e7e9b4e118b3dec9_2152362950058629694.png",
                "id": "talent43767",
                "key": "Bewildering Lights",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Bewildering Lights"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Burst</span><br>Deals 3 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro DMG</span>, summons 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Grin-Malkin Hat</span>, and gains 1 stack of <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Prop Surplus</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Prop Surplus</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Prop Surplus</span> can stack up to 3 times.<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">When this character uses Bewildering Lights:</span> +1 DMG for each <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Prop Surplus</span> stack. After the skill is finalized, consume all <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Prop Surplus</span>, healing 1 HP for this character per stack.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/17/35428890/1f6d82b825fc55a454fe56d6bb68239e_8948421794083718471.png",
                "id": "talent335",
                "key": "Wondrous Trick: Miracle Parade",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Wondrous Trick: Miracle Parade"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Summon</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">End Phase:</span> Deal 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro DMG</span>.<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage(s): 1</span> (Can stack. Max 2 stacks.)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/17/35428890/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_3022392190734144939.png",
                "id": "talent83435",
                "key": "Grin-Malkin Hat",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/17/35428890/0ed08f29bee33744061b306f8acdaf20_4293680251897781368.png",
                "title": "Grin-Malkin Hat"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Applies Pyro and can trigger the following Elemental Reactions:</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\"> </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">]</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Melt</span>: DMG +2 for this instance</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\"> </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">]</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Vaporize</span>: DMG +2 for this instance</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\"> </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">]</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Overloaded</span>: DMG +2 for this instance, the target is forcibly switched to the next character</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\"> </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">]</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Burning</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, creates a [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Burning Flame</span>] that will deal 1 Pyro DMG at the end of the Round (Takes effect once, max 2 stacks)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/17/35428890/d714b3b669cc08d1d8e34464fd7a3630_4626194233537161157.png",
                "id": "talent78471",
                "key": "Pyro DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Pyro DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Physical DMG</span></strong><br>Physical DMG will not apply any Elements, nor can it engage in Elemental Reactions.<br></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Piercing DMG</span></strong><br>Piercing DMG cannot be increased by any bonuses, but cannot be defended against using Shields or DMG Immunity either.</p><p><br><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Usage(s)</span></strong><br>After this card's effect is triggered, 1 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Usage </span>of it will be consumed.<br>This card will be discarded immediately once it has 0 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Usages </span>remaining.<br><br></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/17/35428890/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_3596281600938696581.png",
